'''吉蘭泰龍屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Chilantaisaurus''）是[[獸腳亞目|獸腳亞目]][[新獵龍科|新獵龍科]]下的一[[屬|屬]]，化石發現於[[中國|中國]]的[[蘇紅圖组|蘇紅圖组]]（Suhongtu Formation）<ref name=yangetal2017>{{en}}Yang Jingtao, You Hailu, Xxie Li and Zhou Hongrui(2017)."A New Specimen of Crichtonpelta benxiensis (Dinosauria: Ankylosaurinae) from the Mid-Cretaceous of Liaoning Province, China" [https://www.researchgate.net/publication/318228410_A_New_Specimen_of_Crichtonpelta_benxiensis_Dinosauria_Ankylosaurinae_from_the_Mid-Cretaceous_of_Liaoning_Province_China] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/318228410_A_New_Specimen_of_Crichtonpelta_benxiensis_Dinosauria_Ankylosaurinae_from_the_Mid-Cretaceous_of_Liaoning_Province_China |date=20201112201254 }}</ref>，約1,17至1,04亿年前<ref name=guoetal2018>{{en}}Zhi-Xin Guoa, Yuan-Peng Shib, Yong-Tai Yanga,, Shuan-Qi Jiangb, Lin-Bo Lib, Zhi-Gang Zhao(2018)."Inversion of the Erlian Basin (NE China) in the early Late Cretaceous:Implications for the collision of the Okhotomorsk Block with East Asia" [http://icpms.ustc.edu.cn/laicpms/publications/2018-GuoZX-JAES.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://icpms.ustc.edu.cn/laicpms/publications/2018-GuoZX-JAES.pdf |date=20200919173817 }}</ref>。吉蘭泰龍是種大型恐龍，身長約11~13公尺長，體重估計值介於2.5公噸<ref name=bensonetal2009>Benson, R.B.J., Carrano, M.T and Brusatte, S.L. (2009). "A new clade of archaic large-bodied predatory dinosaurs (Theropoda: Allosauroidea) that survived to the latest Mesozoic." ''Naturwissenschaften'', ''' '''(): . doi:10.1007/s00114-009-0614-x</ref>到4公噸之間<ref name=paul1988>{{cite book|last=Paul |first=G.S. |year=1988 |title=Predatory Dinosaurs of the World |url=https://archive.org/details/predatorydinosau00paul |location=New York |publisher=Simon and Schuster |page= [https://archive.org/details/predatorydinosau00paul/page/314 314]}}</ref>。近年另有研究估計約為6公噸重<ref name=zootaxa>{{Cite journal |author=Brusatte, S.L.; Chure, D.J.; Benson, R.B.J.; Xu, X. |title=The osteology of ''Shaochilong maortuensis'', a carcharodontosaurid (Dinosauria: Theropoda) from the Late Cretaceous of Asia |journal=Zootaxa |volume=2334 |pages=1–46 |year=2010 |url=http://mapress.com/zootaxa/2010/f/z02334p046f.pdf |access-date=2012-03-31 |archive-date=2017-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204124743/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2010/f/z02334p046f.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==分類歷史==
[[模式種|模式種]]是[[大水溝吉蘭泰龍|大水溝吉蘭泰龍]]（''C. tashuikouensis''），於1964年由胡所描述<ref name="hu1964">{{Cite journal|author=SY Hu|year=1964|title=Carnosaurian remains from Alashan, Inner Mongolia|journal=Vertebrata PalAsiatica|volume=8|pages=42-63}}</ref>。他認為牠是屬於[[肉食龍下目|肉食龍下目]]，且與[[異特龍|異特龍]]有接近親緣關係。但後來的多次研究，根據前肢的大型指爪，推測牠是屬於[[棘龍超科|棘龍超科]]，有可能是[[棘龍科|棘龍科]]的原始物種<ref name="sereno1998">{{Cite journal|author= Paul C. Sereno|year=1998|title=A Long-Snouted Predatory Dinosaur from Africa and the Evolution of Spinosaurids|journal=Science|volume=282|issue=5392|pages=1298-1302}}</ref><ref name="chure2002">{{Cite journal|author=Ronan Allain & Daniel J. Chure|year=2002|title=Poekilopleuron bucklandii, the theropod dinosaur from the Middle Jurassic (Bathonian) of Normandy|journal=Palaeontology|volume=45|issue=6|pages=1107-1121}}</ref>。也有研究根據其與[[異特龍超科|異特龍超科]]、棘龍超科、[[虛骨龍類|虛骨龍類]]的相似處，而認為吉蘭泰龍是[[新堅尾龍類|新堅尾龍類]]的未定位屬<ref name=BX08>{{cite journal |last=Benson |first=R.B. |coauthors=Xu, X. |year=2008 |title=The anatomy and systematic position of the theropod dinosaur ''Chilantaisaurus tashuikouensis'' Hu, 1964 from the Early Cretaceous of Alanshan, People's Republic of China |journal=Geological Magazine |doi=10.1017/S0016756808005475 |volume=145|issue=6 }}</ref>。在2009年，新研究發現吉蘭泰龍與肉食龍類的[[假鯊齒龍|假鯊齒龍]]有可能是同種動物，兩者化石發現於不同地層，體型有極大差距<ref name=brusatteetal2009/>。同年的另一份研究，顯示吉蘭泰龍與假鯊齒龍並非同種動物，並將吉蘭泰龍歸類於新建立的[[新獵龍科|新獵龍科]]，是異特龍的近親<ref name=bensonetal2009/>。

除了模式種以外，還有幾個[[種|種]]亦被建立，但都是基於一些很缺乏的遺骸。西伯利亞吉蘭泰龍（''C. sibiricus''）的化石是一節末端[[蹠骨|蹠骨]]，發現於[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[布里亞特共和國|布里亞特共和國]]，地質年代相當於[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]早期的[[巴列姆階|巴列姆階]]到[[豪特里維階|豪特里維階]]。由於化石少，研究描述很不清楚，無法確定這些化石的演化、分類關係<ref name="chure2002" /><ref>Weishampel, David B; et al. (2004). "Dinosaur distribution (Early Cretaceous, Asia)." In: Weishampel, David B.; Dodson, Peter; and Osmólska, Halszka (eds.): The Dinosauria, 2nd, Berkeley: University of California Press. Pp. 563-570. ISBN 978-0-520-24209-8.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://home.comcast.net/~eoraptor/Carnosauria.htm%23Chilantaisaurussibiricus |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-06-30 |archive-date=2012-06-30 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120630212336/home.comcast.net/~eoraptor/Carnosauria.htm%23Chilantaisaurussibiricus |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[毛儿图吉兰泰龙|毛儿图吉兰泰龙]]（''C. maortuensis''）有可能是原始的[[虛骨龍類|虛骨龍類]][[恐龍|恐龍]]<ref name="chure2002" />，已在2009年被建立為[[假鯊齒龍|假鯊齒龍]]<ref name=brusatteetal2009>Brusatte, S., Benson, R., Chure, D., Xu, X., Sullivan, C., and Hone, D. (2009). "The first definitive carcharodontosaurid (Dinosauria: Theropoda) from Asia and the delayed ascent of tyrannosaurids." ''Naturwissenschaften'', DOI: 10.1007/s00114-009-0565-2</ref>。[[浙江吉兰泰龙|浙江吉兰泰龙]]（''C. zheziangensis''）的骨頭則是來自[[鐮刀龍超科|鐮刀龍超科]]，可能事實上是來自於[[南雄龍|南雄龍]][[模式標本|模式標本]]的同一個體。

